{"tid":2239397,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高銀金融遭德意志信託入稟申請清盤","createTime":"2020-10-12T01:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T01:51:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fb50adc6e6e1bc0d99d2f827f958b7f2901b99","tid":2239397,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T01:42:07.000Z","msg":"高銀金融遭德意志信託入稟申請清盤<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2605446/%E9%AB%98%E9%8A%80%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%81%AD%E5%BE%B7%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97%E4%BF%A1%E8%A8%97%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2605446%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25BF%2597%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25A8%2597%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%259B%25A4&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBYDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=5585fd74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2605446/%E9%AB%98%E9%8A%80%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%81%AD%E5%BE%B7%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97%E4%BF%A1%E8%A8%97%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n高銀金融(00530)公布，10月7日自百慕達代理人收到郵件，隨件附上呈請人德意志信託於8月7日向百慕達最高法院提呈針對公司之清盤呈請副本。該呈請答辯日期定為10月9日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司稱，基於無充足時間充分理解該呈請之影響，已透過香港律師事務所，指示百慕達法律顧問就該呈請提供意見，並出席定於10月9日舉行之聆訊。呈請聆訊隨後押後至10月30日。百慕達高等法院首席大法官亦頒令雙方須於下一次聆訊前的特定日期提交證據。公司將就該呈請作出抗辯。<br />\n<br />\n此外，公司又接獲德意志信託通知，已委任接管人到持有九龍灣高銀金融國際中心的兩家公司。公司現正就接管的影響徵詢法律意見。德意志信託為高銀債權人之一。"},{"pid":"cb6fbb43c7d3176cdc88fda76a95c0711ad9e3b5","tid":2239397,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}